#. module: project_timesheet_holidays
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/project_timesheet_holidays/models/account_analytic.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot create timesheets for a task that is linked to a time off type. "
"Please use the Time Off application to request new time off instead."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດສ້າງໃບລາຍງານເວລາສຳລັບໜ້າວຽກທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບປະເພດການລາພັກ. ກະລຸນາໃຊ້ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ ການ"
"ລາພັກ ເພື່ອຮ້ອງຂໍການລາພັກໃໝ່ແທນ."

#. module: project_timesheet_holidays
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/project_timesheet_holidays/models/account_analytic.py:0
msgid "You cannot delete timesheets that are linked to global time off."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບໃບລາຍງານເວລາທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບການລາພັກແບບທົ່ວໄປໄດ້."

#. module: project_timesheet_holidays
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/project_timesheet_holidays/models/account_analytic.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot delete timesheets that are linked to time off requests. Please "
"cancel your time off request from the Time Off application instead."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບໃບລາຍງານເວລາທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍລາພັກໄດ້. ກະລຸນາຍົກເລີກຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍລາພັກຂອງທ່ານຈາກແ"
"ອັບພລິເຄຊັນ ການລາພັກ ແທນ."

#. module: project_timesheet_holidays
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/project_timesheet_holidays/models/account_analytic.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot modify timesheets that are linked to time off requests. Please "
"use the Time Off application to modify your time off requests instead."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໃບລາຍງານເວລາທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍລາພັກໄດ້. ກະລຸນາໃຊ້ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ ການລາພັກ ເພື່ອ"
"ແກ້ໄຂຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍລາພັກຂອງທ່ານແທນ."
